hikari pins  virtual   threads  because of synchronized keyword;;

need to use modern libraries to avoid platform thread pinning:
// PINS in JDK 21-23
HikariCP hikariCP = new HikariCP();

// NO PINNING in JDK 21-23
Agroal agroal = new Agroal(); // Built for virtual threads

// PINS in JDK 21-23
Apache HttpClient 4.x -- needs to be removed***

// NO PINNING in JDK 21-23
Apache HttpClient 5.x  // Uses ReentrantLock internally
JDK HttpClient         // No synchronized blocks